PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?item WHERE { ?item a <http://www.wikidata.org/ontology#Movie> ; <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P17> <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q147> . }

natural_language_question: To which countries does the Himalayan mountain system extend?
sparql_query:
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
`SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q30> <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P17> ?uri }`

natural_language_question: What is the largest country in the world?
sparql_query:
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri wdt:P31 wdt:P17 ; wdt:P2046 ?n . FILTER( !BOUND(?n) ) } ORDER BY DESC(?n) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1
